title: 01/16 Fantasy Football Podcast: Playoffs Winners & Losers; Offseason Questions
description:
Let's start with some winners and losers after the Divisional round of the NFL Playoffs. We're talking Stefon Diggs (7:30), Brandin Cooks (9:08), Leonard Fournette (10:50), JAC WRs (15:35) and more ... Latest coaching news from around the NFL (24:30) ... We've got an offseason question for each eliminated team: ATL (32:25), NO and PIT (37:15), TEN (42:55), LAR (44:30), KC (47:55), BUF (49:05), CAR (49:45) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
